abstract: >-
  A native Rust and CUDA runtime for progressive Qwen3-TTS 1.7B VoiceDesign
  inference on NVIDIA DGX Spark, with an HTTP API, embedded model artifacts,
  reproducible qualification evidence, and a hardened ARM64 container image.
